native_setup.description:
This is the source-mapping section of the Zero Net Export command center. Sensors owns mapped roles and source health. Use this screen for solar, grid, battery, and source-freshness work, not managed-device promotion or controller-policy tuning. First choose whether your grid sensors are exposed as one combined signed/net source or as separate import/export entities.

