Current source health: {source_health}
Recommended next step: {source_next_step}

Primary path: {configure_path}.

native_setup_sources.description:
Map the required entities and set the refresh interval. Sensors owns source repair and source-health work, so keep fleet onboarding in Managed Devices and controller tuning in Controls instead of here. Grid mode: {grid_mode}. {grid_mapping_note} Use the native selectors first. If Combined / net grid energy or Battery state of charge still triggers Home Assistant's `Entity is neither a valid entity ID nor a valid UUID` validation on a valid choice, first capture the exact error or a screenshot, then clear that selector, paste the same entity ID into the matching fallback field below, and save again.

